      "text": "The truth lies within your lies, lies within you",
      "start": 151.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 160.39999389648438,
      "text": "The truth lies within you",
      "start": 156.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 162.4199981689453,
      "text": "In the night you fight",
      "start": 160.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 165.27999877929688,
      "text": "Everything you thought was positive was the best",
      "start": 162.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 169.6999969482422,
      "text": "But then you come back around and don't even try to",
      "start": 165.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 174.82000732421875,
      "text": "Heal the seal, the feel of your momentary come up",
      "start": 169.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 177.10000610351562,
      "text": "Are you for real?",
      "start": 174.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 181.3800048828125,
      "text": "Yeah",
      "start": 180.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 185.72000122070312,
      "text": "Lies are the truth, the truth in your lies",
      "start": 181.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 190.6199951171875,
      "text": "I'll see you on the other side",
      "start": 187.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 193.97999572753906,
      "text": "Just don't bring that disguise that hides",
      "start": 190.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 196.22000122070312,
      "text": "That curates your existence",
      "start": 193.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 199.10000610351562,
      "text": "Try to break above that",
      "start": 196.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 201.33999633789062,
      "text": "God is in your truth",
      "start": 199.10000610351562
    },
    {
